--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : countries management
Scenario name   : add country 
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Nazioni" and then "Aggiungi".
4. Insert values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The new country is added to the system.
2. ID and NAME are required fields.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : countries management
Scenario name   : modify country 
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert a country as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Modifica" in the countries list page, for the country 
   just inserted.
6. Change the values and press the button "Conferma".

Expected results:

1. The country is correctly changed.
2. The field ID is not editable.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : countries management
Scenario name   : delete country 
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert a country as in scenario 1.
5. Select the link "Cancella" and confirm the deletion.

Expected results:

1. The country is correctly deleted.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 4
Use case        : countries management
Scenario name   : paging
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Insert 25 countries repeating 25 times scenario 1.
5. Verify the paging adding, removing end changing the countries.

Expected results:

1. The countries paging works fine.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 5
Use case        : countries management
Scenario name   : unauthorized access
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Insert the following url in the browser address txt box:
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminListCountries.do
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminAddCountries.do
		http://<host>:<port>/<context>/adminEditCountries.do

Expected results:

1. The following message is displayed:
	"Autorizzazione non consentita. L'operazione richiesta necessita delle 
	credenziali di amministratore."
